11).Block Elements are those elements that takes up the whole width of the screen.
12).<span> tag is used to occupy only the needed space.
13).Margin : It is the space outside the boarder of an element. It creates space between the boarder of an element and adjacent elements.
14).Padding : It is the space inside the boarder of the element. It creats space between the content of the element and its boarder.
